projects.description: Language of implementation :- Python Driver fatigue is one of the major causes of accidents in the world. Detecting the drowsiness of driver is one of the surest ways of measuring driver fatigue. In this project we aim to develop a prototype drowsiness detection system. This system works by monitoring the eyes of driver and sounding an alarm when he/she is drowsy.
